summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fourteenth Avenue West from the north margin of West Grove Street to North margin of Gilman Avenue et al., in the City of Seattle., by constructing concrete & wood sidewalks under Ordinance No. 21370, creating Local Improvement District No. 2126 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
